Project Summary:

This project is an Agentic AI-based system that automates job application assistance for users.
It allows users to register, log in, upload resumes, and provide job descriptions through a web interface.
The system extracts features like skills from resumes and calculates a match score using basic NLP techniques.
Based on extracted skills, it intelligently suggests relevant jobs and internships from online platforms.
The application is built using HTML, CSS, JavaScript for frontend and Python (Flask) for backend integration.

Use of This Project
💡 Main Purpose

👉 The project helps users automate and simplify the job search and application process using AI.

🔧 Key Uses
1. ⏳ Saves Time
Instead of manually searching jobs
👉 System suggests relevant jobs automatically
2. 🎯 Better Job Matching
Compares resume with job description
👉 Gives match score
👉 Helps user know if they are suitable
3. 🧠 Skill Identification
Extracts skills from resume
👉 Helps users understand their strengths
4. 💼 Job & Internship Recommendations
Suggests roles based on skills
👉 Example:
Python → Python Developer
ML → ML Intern
5. 🚀 Helps Freshers (Very Important)
Students don’t know where to apply
👉 This system guides them automatically


